<?php
return ['messages'=>['<h2 class="post_title entry-title"><a href="https://eji.com.hk/butt-litter-clean-up-day-2023/">SMOKE-FREE HONG KONG: Butt Litter Clean-Up Day 2023</a></h2>'=>'<h2 class="post_title entry-title"><a href="https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e7%84%a1%e7%85%99%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%ef%bc%9a2023%e5%b9%b4%e6%b8%85%e6%8e%83%e5%9e%83%e5%9c%be%e6%97%a5/">無煙香港：2023年清掃垃圾日</a></h2>','<p><strong><big>Follow us</big></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><big>關注我們</big></strong></p>','<p>As a proud<strong> jewellery manufacturer</strong>, we extend our heartfelt gratitude to <a href="https://www.loksintong.org/"><strong>Lok Sin Tong</strong></a> for organizing this inspiring event. Their dedication to supporting those in need inspires us to continue our journey of spreading love,  positivity, and care throughout the community.</p><p>Let’s all embrace the spirit of giving this Chinese New Year and beyond!</p>'=>'<p>作為一家負責任<strong>珠寶製造商</strong>，EJI由衷感謝<a href="https://www.loksintong.org/"><strong>樂善堂</strong></a>主辦這項溫暖人心的活動。<br><br><br> 樂善堂對有需要人士的支持與奉獻精神，鼓勵我們繼續在社區傳播愛與關懷。</p><p>讓我們在這個農曆新年及未來，共同擁抱給予的精神。</p>','<p>As a responsible and caring <strong>jewellery manufacturer in Hong Kong</strong>, we are committed to giving back to our community. With the Chinese New Year just around the corner, we once again joined hands with<a href="https://www.loksintong.org/"><strong> Lok Sin Tong</strong></a> for the second year in a row in this meaningful initiative to spread love and warmth to the elderly. This year’s<strong> lucky bag distribution event</strong> took place on Saturday, 18 January 2025.</p>'=>'<p>作為一家<strong>植根香港的負責任珠寶製造商</strong>，EJI致力回饋社會。 隨著農曆新年即將來臨，我們連續第二年與<a href="https://www.loksintong.org/"><strong> 樂善堂</strong></a> 攜手合作，為長者傳遞愛與溫暖。 今年的<strong> 福袋分發活動</strong> 於 2025 年 1 月 18 日星期六舉行。</p>','<p>Our dedicated volunteering team of 8 members, including our staff and their young family members, enthusiastically participated in this heartwarming activity. Together, we distributed lucky bags filled with blessings and goodwill, and essential items, bringing joy and companionship to the elderly residents in the neighborhood.  The smiles on the faces of both the elderly and our volunteers were truly priceless, a touching reminder of the power of connection and care.</p>'=>'<p>由8名成員組成的熱心義工團隊，包括公司員工和他們的年輕家庭成員，熱情地參與了這項暖心活動。 我們一同派發裝滿祝福與善意的福袋，內含生活必需品，為社區內的長者帶來歡樂與陪伴。 長者與義工臉上的笑容無比珍貴，提醒我們連結與關懷的力量是多麼重要。</p>','<p>We are incredibly grateful to be part of this meaningful event. Participating in this event was more than just an act of giving – it was always a humbling and rewarding experience to give back, especially during festive seasons likes Chinese New Year, when togetherness and community matter most.</p>'=>'<p>我們很高興能參與這項有意義的活動。 福袋派發不僅是單純的給予，更是一次謙卑且充實的體驗，尤其當農曆新年臨近，團聚與社區聯繫顯得尤為重要。</p>','A Humbling and Rewarding Experience'=>'一次充實的體驗','About Lok Sin Tong'=>'關於樂善堂','Founded in 1880, The Sin Tong Benevolent Society, Kowloon (Lok Sin Tong) is one of the oldest and most respected charitable organization in Hong Kong. 
They are committed to providing essential medical services, educational support, and social welfare programs to individuals and families in need. 
Their mission spans generations, fostering a spirit of care, compassion, and solidarity.
'=>'樂善堂（Lok Sin Tong） 成立於 1880 年，是香港歷史最悠久的慈善機構之一。 
樂善堂致力於為有需要人士與家庭提供醫療服務、教育支援和社會福利計劃； 
樂善堂秉持關愛、慈悲與團結精神，跨越世代，服務社會。
','Read More'=>'閱讀更多','description_text-image-box-f5a9acc'=>'樂善堂（Lok Sin Tong） 成立於 1880 年，是香港歷史最悠久的慈善機構之一。 
樂善堂致力於為有需要人士與家庭提供醫療服務、教育支援和社會福利計劃； 
樂善堂秉持關愛、慈悲與團結精神，跨越世代，服務社會。
